DsU0ChNLhyX2P6g0WLNA0Bd8SSH8otlkXdkWHfw&oe=670F941D"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot(2)_2560_1440.png", "id": "1154233268797591", "uri": "https://scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982571_1154233272130924_4529887224270705141_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=no_JxfTPk0wQ7kNvgEZIfOi&_nc_ht=scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA5RNbMkXYD7Eu5_4twbkHjVjztBGWP355qjg3pV_Rq1A&oe=670F8BF2"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot(1)_2560_1440.png", "id": "2100665936973153", "uri": "https://scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982680_2100665940306486_5664456920141678252_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=oFFCDXtRf28Q7kNvgFlyRBt&_nc_ht=scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCBY28AJc0RONu2xlW9YTKznHTE5jdHd-3GE4fWkKGQaw&oe=670FB157"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Cover Image.png", "id": "368600119311127", "uri": "https://scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001730_368600122644460_5598028405797075028_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Z6kRGtMHOwcQ7kNvgGkqNEw&_nc_ht=scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDyr6WTD3vrjx0a5hxI9-ejYJoewPBFJxRwsMmuvw_TQg&oe=670FB695"}, "display_name": "2035 Carbon neutrality of smart green city", "keywords": [], "long_description": "It is a VR content that allows teenagers to experience a space for carbon neutrality, learn about the need for carbon neutrality, what they can do, and explore future career paths.\n\n1. Experience goal\n- Discover specific career topics in promising future industries and occupations against the backdrop of a smart green city in 2035\n- Explore a future path by experiencing a space for carbon neutrality\n- Learn about the need for carbon neutrality and what young people can do\n- Learn about core underlying technologies such as realistic content technology provided as an experience\n\n2. Characteristics of content\n- First-person perspective in which the experiencer becomes the main character\n- 7-step composition according to the actual experience process\n- Developed based on standing only\n- Movement and manipulation using the Oculus Controller\n- Estimated experience time of about 20 to 30 minutes\n\n3. 7-step configuration\nSTEP 1 Instructions on how to operate\nSTEP 2 Meeting with the UN Youth Delegation\nSTEP 3 Practicing carbon neutrality in urban forests\nSTEP 4 Implementation of carbon neutrality in wind power plants\nSTEP 5 Carbon neutrality practice at the East Coast carbon storage site\nSTEP 6 Think\nSTEP 7 Finishing\n", "short_description": "It is a VR content that allows teenagers to experience a space for carbon neutrality, learn about the need for carbon neutrality, what they can do, and explore future career paths."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "HeroCover_3000x900.png", "id": "7527653000591853", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001730_7527653007258519_8435369833685824333_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YoeB0w_itGwQ7kNvgHvLHD1&_nc_ht=scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAoVgoFbESqYnVZA0tbQekwPG0o9-wXvWdLa2O44XLhPg&oe=670F9202"}, {"file_name": "Landscape_2560x1440.png", "id": "1452940842279363", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031355_1452940845612696_1891464877969558457_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=h6e9MOBzqDkQ7kNvgE2p4XM&_nc_ht=scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYArB6GsoDifXA0AbrSir90l-A202kaNaUOa6NnZXfdIwA&oe=670FB0C4"}, {"file_name": "Portrait_1008x1440.png", "id": "959181839136200", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57566686_959181842469533_2388841801262298119_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=dQvoYtjalRAQ7kNvgEh9wMR&_nc_ht=scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDMtIZQILPzZM6yDpJGhUFUByKX1zfZNbX8htC8cmoEfQ&oe=670FA922"}, {"file_name": "Icon_512x512.png", "id": "874968081049627", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https